 | accessdate=2008-04-30
 }}</ref>
{{-}}

== 2008 Festival ==
The [[World Science Festival, 2008|inaugural World Science Festival]] took place from May 28 to June 1, 2008, at 22&nbsp;venues throughout New York City. It included 46&nbsp;events, a street fair and, on its first day, the one-day World Science Summit at Columbia University. The Festival was attended by 120,000&nbsp;people.<ref>Venues and event numbers: {{Citation
